judges: Add a module to clean stale kernel files

judges: Protect currently running kernel from removal

Add a ProtectRunning judge that prevents removal of the currently
running kernel. The main goal is to keep the modules directory from
being removed while the kernel is still running, even if the main
kernel files have been cleansed already.
